 "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012640, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Apni izzat ke ehaate (daaire) aur bachaaw ki hifaazat mein naagahaani (achaanak aane waali) aafato’n se aur jald aane waali pareshaaniyo’n se, ay Ma’bood! ay Rab Tu balaawo’n ki sar-zameen ko neeche dansa (daba) de sakhtiyo’n ke maidaan ko ukhaad de, museebato’n ke suraj ko gehna (mita) de, buraayi ke pahaado’n ko tod de, zamaane ke dukho’n ko dur kar de, kaamo’n ki rukaawato’n ko hata de.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!اپنی عزّت کے احاطے اور بچاؤ کی حفاظت میں ناگہانی آفتوں سے اور جلد آنے والی پریشانیوں سے اے معبود! اے رب تو بلاؤں کی سرزمین کو نیچے دھنسا دے سختیوں کے میدان کو اکھاڑ دے مصیبتوں کے سورج کو گہنا دے برائی کے پہاڑوں کو توڑدے زمانے کےکرب کو دور کردے کامو ں کی رکاوٹوں کو ہٹا دے۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ فِىْ حِيَاطَةِ عِزِّكَ وَحِفَاظِ حِرْزِكَ مِنْ مُبَاغَتَةِ الدَّوَايِرِ وَمُعَاجَلَةِ الْبَوَادِرِ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ رَبِّ وَاَرْضَ الْبَلَاءِ فَاَخْسِفْهَا وَعَرْصَةَ الْمِحَنِ فَارْجُفْهَا وَشَمْسَ النَّوَاۗئِبِ فَاكْسِفْهَا وَجِبَالَ السُّوْءِ فَانْسِفْهَا وَكُرَبَ الدَّهْرِ فَاكْشِفْهَا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012641, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mujhe salaamati ke hauzo’n (bunker) mein pohoncha de, mujhe aabroo ki sawaariyo’n par sawaar kar de, gunaho’n se bachne mein mera saath de, mujhe pardah-poshi mein shaamil kar le, mujh par sakhaawat farma ay Rab apni ne’mato’n ki balaaye’n dur karne ki aur apni sakhtiya’n dur rakhne ki, mujh se apne tamaam azaab dur farma, apni sakht sazaawo’n ka rukh mod de, mujhe zamaane ki bad-haaliyo’n se panah de.", "Urdu": "مجھے سلامتی کے حوضوں میں پہنچا دے مجھے آبرو کی سواریوں پر سوار کردے گناہوں سے بچنے میں میرا ساتھ دے مجھے پردہ پوشی میں شامل کرلے مجھ پر سخاوت فرما اے رب اپنی نعمتوں کی بلائیں دور کرنے کی اور اپنی سختیاں دور رکھنے کی مجھ سے اپنے تمام عذاب دور فرما اپنی سخت سزاؤں کا رخ موڑ دے مجھے زمانے کی بدحالیوں سے پناہ دے۔", "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَعَوَاۗئِقَ الْاُمُوْرِ فَاصْرِفْهَا وَاَوْرِدْنِىْ حِيَاضَ السَّلَامَةِ وَاحْمِلْنِىْ عَلٰى مَطَايَا الْكَرَامَةِ وَاصْحَبْنِىْ بِاِقَالَةِ الْعَثْرَةِ وَاشْمَلْنِىْ بِسِتْرِ الْعَوْرَةِ وَجُدْ عَلَىَّ يا رَبِّ بِالَّائِكَ وَكَشْفِ بَلَّائِكَ وَدَفْعِ ضَرَّاۗئِكَ وَادْفَعْ عَنِّىْ كَلَاكِلَ عَذَابِكَ وَاصْرِفْ عَنِّى اَلِيْمَ عِقَابِكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedS